CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1945, pg. 17, reads: "Blind Coach - Morris Taylor, with three of his 'Crunkleton Bears' - Ed Macon and Jack Harris, halfbacks; Carl Younger, quarterback.  Taylor says: 'I'm priming my boys to beat the 'Eagles' this year. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Crunkleton Bears football coach Morris Taylor with players Ed Macon, Jack Harris, and Carl Younger posed in Harris Studio
